
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <style>
        #about {
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding-top: 90px;
            padding-bottom:45px;
        }
        #about .div-img-bg {
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border: 20px solid #b8a07e;
        }
        #about .div-img-bg .about-img img {
            width: 100%;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 85px 0px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.14);
            margin-top: -60px;
            margin-left: 40px;
            height: 400px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        #about .about-descr .p-heading {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        #about .about-descr .separator {
            max-width: 80%;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            text-align: left;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- start section about us -->
    <div class="container" id="about">
        <div class="row justify-content-between">

            <div class="col-lg-4 ">
                <div class="div-img-bg">
                    <div class="about-img">
                        <img src="~/IMGs/me.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="me" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-7">
                <div class="about-descr">

                    <p class="p-heading">I'm a North Carolina based web developer who loves clean, simple & unique design. I also enjoy digital artistry, ui/ux creation, & logo design. </p>
                    <p class="separator">Raised with computers, I found a passion for all things digital at an early age. Over the years I've delved into all the different aspects of coding, digital art, & web production.</p>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    @section scripts{
        @*script to change the masthead stuff*@
        <script>
            $(document).ready(function () {
                // Set background image of a div on load
                var imageUrl = "/IMGs/about-bg.jpg";
                $(".masthead").css("background-image", "url(" + imageUrl + ")");
                $('#topText').text("About");
                $('#subText').text("Let's talk about me");
            });
        </script>
    }

</body>

</html>

